        <h6>Status for <span class="text-primary">RFP-2025-001</span></h6>
        <ul class="list-group">
          <li class="list-group-item">Submission Received ✅</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">Technical Evaluation ⏳</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">Financial Evaluation ❌ (Not Yet)</li>
          <li class="list-group-item">Final Decision ❌ (Pending)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

